{
  "stem": "766.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they-- we-- we assume that, so they thought we are run away, outlaws, which parent let go.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they had suspicions.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But with the time, they learned.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They learned, or rather before I came, there were others, so they had already an idea that this isn't so bad.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, probably my father provided that we should have the French currency available, that we have to go to a bank to change.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He probably changed it there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was-- it is 70 years ago.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Wait, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To the faculty.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, to the faculty, yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in France, I have to say, I didn't have all the years.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It took eight years, through '33 from '26, so seven years.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't have any difficulty of the question being Jewish.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It never came out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They never asked, I never said.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know whether they were so aware.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When I came to France, I thought everybody's Jewish, because they are dark, they are short, and they are gesticulate.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I thought they are Jews.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But what I want to emphasize, they are not too friendly to foreigners.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "No students, girl or boy, eventually, invited to a home, not even Jewish.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But they are against foreigners.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I didn't feel any difficulties in this respect.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't meet too much.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not only I, none of us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because the French, they don't-- the students, they are poor.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They all think they are poor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Doesn't mean that everybody was so poor, but they don't socialize with foreigners.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So that's all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Among students-- among students-- I socialized mostly with Polish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From all over the country.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not from my town, necessarily.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not-- nobody.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't remember now.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we kept together.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
